      "writtenOn": "2020-10-21T12:36:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Statement-expressions seem like a poor fit for Skia, since they aren\u0027t standard C++ and don\u0027t compile at all on MSVC. This particular block is iOS-only so it would work, but it seems... out of place to me? I dunno, I would rather keep it as standard-compliant C++ across the board. A lambda could work I guess, if you still think that\u0027s an improvement.",
